nodes.text: A male individual resided on the planet Serenno during the time of the Galactic Republic. When Count Gora of Serenno brought in a number of droids to replace jobs done by the people, the resident joined a group of other protestors at the funeral of Countess Anya on Serenno's funeral moon of Mantero, interrupting a speech made by Lady Jenza. Gora set his security droids on the protestors, but the Jedi Padawan Dooku intervened.
